section.p:
We recommend a modern desktop or notebook computer with 1-2 GB of RAM or more and a dual core or more CPU for the teacher workstation. A more powerful computer is recommended if one or more of the following is required:


more than 20 students in the class;

class equipped with a wireless network;

several video streams (particularly HD video) used as media sources simultaneously;

video (particularly HD video) from external sources used as a media source;
